productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Allean has one of these. She works as a sky diver and she says it looks weedy.
The box this comes in is 5 kilometer by 5 inch and weights 13 kilogram!!!
I saw one of these in South Korea and I bought one.
This fresh-thinking works excessively well. It mortally improves my golf by a lot.
i use it every Tuesday when i'm in my homeless shelter.
